## What We Got Right ✅

- RSI zone filter (30/70) is indeed a quality gate — confirmed and kept
- The 5-bar delay issue was real and important — we solved it by making `lbR` configurable and reducing it to 1–3
- Regular divergences only — we confirmed hidden divergences are excluded by design for now

